Uses of Package
javax.cache.integration

  • Packages that use javax.cache.integration 
    Package Description
    javax.cache
    This package contains the API for JCache.
    javax.cache.configuration
    This package contains configuration classes and interfaces.
    javax.cache.integration
    This package contains interfaces for integration.
  • Classes in javax.cache.integration used by javax.cache 
    Class and Description
    CompletionListener
    A CompletionListener is implemented by an application when it needs to be notified of the completion of some Cache operation.
  • Classes in javax.cache.integration used by javax.cache.configuration 
    Class and Description
    CacheLoader
    Used when a cache is read-through or when loading data into a cache via the Cache.loadAll(java.util.Set, boolean, CompletionListener) method.
    CacheWriter
    A CacheWriter is used for write-through to an external resource.
  • Classes in javax.cache.integration used by javax.cache.integration 
    Class and Description
    CacheLoaderException
    An exception to indicate a problem has occurred executing a CacheLoader.
    CacheWriterException
    An exception to indicate a problem has occurred executing a CacheWriter.
    CompletionListener
    A CompletionListener is implemented by an application when it needs to be notified of the completion of some Cache operation.
